text: Stone Lake is in Stone Lake State Park, a California State Park, located in Sacramento County, California. The open space property protects two rare natural Central Valley lakes and their surrounding riparian habitat and grassland areas. The County of Sacramento operates Stone Lake. == External links == *Official Stone Lake State Park site Category:State parks of California Category:Lakes of Sacramento County, California Category:Lakes of California Category:Parks in the San Joaquin Valley Category:Parks in Sacramento County, California
